    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like i'm being forced to carry it. why does the universe require us to suffer through this awareness? if it's all so empty and indifferent, then why is there even this pressure to keep going? it feels like the only logical response to the absurdity is to just... stop. it seems more rational to just opt out than to keep fighting a fight that has no point.",
